The League Cup Show
Wednesday 24th September 2014 

As the League Cup reaches the last 16, Round 3, the featured match sees the 2013 Cup winners welcome former manager Roberto Martinez back to the Liberty as Swansea take on Everton. Plus extended highlights from White Hart Lane, as Tottenham meet Stuart Pearce's Nottingham Forest and Liverpool go head-to-head with Middlesbrough.
